APPLICATION DEVELOPMENT PROJECT
Project Title

Student Management System

Objective

To develop a Python-based application for managing student records efficiently.

Features
Add Student
View Students
Search Student
Delete Student
User Friendly Menu
Technologies Used
Python 3
VS Code
Working

The application allows users to manage student records through a menu-driven interface. Users can add, search, view, and delete student information.

Conclusion

This project demonstrates the use of Python classes, lists, dictionaries, and functions to build a practical application. It is a portfolio-ready project for beginners.